		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You can also put a batch file in the project's directory that opens up a new prompt with everything set everything up properly when you double-click it. This one I use for building 32X/Saturn stuff.. It opens up a new prompt located in the batch file's directory with the SH2 toolchain temporarily added to the path.
<br />
<br /><strong>Set PATH=C:\PROGRA~1\KPITCU~1\GNUSHV~1\sh-elf\bin;C:\PROGRA~1\KPITCU~1\GNUSHV~1\OtherU~1;%PATH%<br />Set MAKE_MODE=unix<br /><br />Cmd "cd\" /k</strong>

		

